      "span_text": "A recent review article proposes an indepth examination of the physicochemical properties of engineered nanomaterials that may impact their ability to interact with the nervous system, reporting how they contribute to nanoparticle distribution in the brain as well as how they may induce effects on it, bringing further evidence of possible nano-brain interactions  ."
